## 14. Dot Mac (.mdc) Rules Configuration

`.mdc` (Markdown Config) files tell Claude Code and Roo Code how to behave in your project.

### Step 14.1 — Create the rules folder

```bash
mkdir -p .cursor/rules
# Also works as:
mkdir -p .claude/rules
