### Claude Code CLI Additions

```bash
# Task Master AI (already installed above)
npm install -g task-master-ai

# Claude Code MCP filesystem tools
# (built-in, no install needed)

# Prettier for auto-formatting
npm install --save-dev prettier eslint eslint-plugin-react
```

### VS Code Extensions (Extended List)

Beyond what was in Section 3, also install:

| Extension | Why |
|---|---|
| **Cursor** (if switching) | Even more AI-native editor |
| **GitHub Copilot** | Secondary AI for inline suggestions |
| **Peacock** | Color-codes your workspace window |
| **TODO Highlight** | Highlights TODO/FIXME in code |
| **Indent Rainbow** | Colors indent levels |
| **Bracket Pair Colorizer** | Colors matching brackets |
| **Live Server** | Quick HTML preview |
| **npm Intellisense** | Autocomplete npm packages |
| **Version Lens** | Shows latest package versions in package.json |
| **Import Cost** | Shows bundle size of imports inline |
| **Turbo Console Log** | Smarter console.log snippets |

### Roo Code Plugins (within Roo Code settings)

In Roo Code sidebar → **Modes** → Enable:
- `Code` mode — for writing code
- `Architect` mode — for planning structure
- `Ask` mode — for questions about code
- `Debug` mode — for fixing bugs

Set **API Provider** in Roo Code → OpenRouter → paste your OpenRouter key → select `google/gemini-flash-1.5` for free tier.

---

