## 19. Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| `electron` not found | `npm install --save-dev electron` |
| White screen on launch | Check Vite is running on port 5173 first |
| Folder dialog doesn't open | Confirm `contextIsolation: true` and preload is loading |
| AI scan returns empty | Check `.env` has correct VITE_ prefix on all keys |
| `pip` not found | Use `pip3` instead; or full path on Windows |
| Terminal output not streaming | Confirm `onCommandOutput` listener is registered before `runCommand` |
| Task Master not connecting | Run `claude /mcp` to verify MCP connection |
| App won't build | Check `electron-builder` is installed: `npm i -D electron-builder` |
| `.mdc` rules not applying | Confirm Roo Code has rules path set in Settings → Rules |

